    complete 100
    depends participant_ui.part_graph_view.part_entity_detail_panel_chromatic_axiom_mark_badge, audience.aud_graph_rendering
    note -8<-
      Lift the moderator's `apps/moderator/src/graph/AxiomMarkBadge.tsx` and the participant's `apps/participant/src/detail/AxiomMarkBadge.tsx` into `packages/shell/src/facet-pill/` (or a sibling directory) as a single `<AxiomMarkBadge>` export once the audience surface materializes as the third caller. Today the moderator is the first caller (canvas-side per-node badge row) and the participant is the second caller (entity detail panel axiom-mark attribution row — landed in this leaf). Deferred-until-third-caller policy: extracting at two callers risks ossifying the wrong prop shape (participant takes `screenName: string` because it has the roster; moderator takes `mark: AxiomMark` because it doesn't yet). When the audience surface adds a third call site the convergence point is clear.

      Scope: align the prop shape across both existing implementations, lift the component into packages/shell/src/ with full vitest coverage, replace both local copies with imports from @a-conversa/shell, drop any cross-app deps this extraction makes redundant. No protocol or wire-format change; no methodology change.

      Source: tasks/refinements/participant-ui/part_entity_detail_panel_chromatic_axiom_mark_badge.md + commit landing that task.
    ->8-
  }

